{"tid":2259413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無惧中國制裁，美批准對台售100套「魚叉」岸防導彈系統 價值$187億","createTime":"2020-10-26T22:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:22:50.000Z","uid":239336,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0ac3e652f8388bddebac0f40f02363394140ff","tid":2259413,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T22:52:51.000Z","msg":"美國國務院周一批准對台灣出售100套波音公司生產的「魚叉」（Harpoon）岸防導彈系統，價值24億美元（187億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n國務院表示，「魚叉」系統有助改善採購者的安全，協助維持地區政治穩定、軍事平衡、經濟發展。<br />\n<br />\n台灣國防資深人士早前透露，政府將向美方爭取更多數量的岸置魚叉導彈，作為台灣「岸防巡航導彈系統」（Coastal Defense Cruise Missile， CDCM），並搭配台軍現有的岸置型雄二、雄三反艦導彈，可將擊殺共艦率從50%提升至70%，確保台海安全。<br />\n<br />\n路透社早前報道，美國近期將對台出售7項軍備。美國國防安全合作署（DSCA）上周三表示，國務院已經批准對出售波音生產的遠程陸攻導彈（SLAM-ER）、洛歇馬丁公司（Lockheed Martin）生產的遠程精準火力打擊系統「海馬斯」（HIMARS）與F-16新式偵照莢艙（MS-110），並已正式知會國會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201027/WFSLVQ7A6NELVEOVEG2RD6R7P4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201027%2FWFSLVQ7A6NELVEOVEG2RD6R7P4%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=aa59b068\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201027%2FWFSLVQ7A6NELVEOVEG2RD6R7P4%2F&h=22b7cea3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201027/WFSLVQ7A6NELVEOVEG2RD6R7P4/</a>"},{"pid":"174fc168970134f481047d112ded484111cbae2f","tid":2259413,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T22:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6482bb79c7e1b92c96f4878331c3563e34dbb1","tid":2259413,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T23:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/l